      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next big adventure? This beauty has been so good to me and is still running like an absolute champ. It\u2019s in really solid shape, super clean inside, and honestly just a total joy to drive. I\u2019m a bit sad to see it go, but I know it\u2019s going to make its next owner very happy! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself\u2014you're going to love it!",
