    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s high-revving masterpiece. Powered by the S54 3.2L inline-six featuring six individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, it delivers visceral, linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis has been enhanced with essential rear subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings to maintain torsional rigidity. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive valve clearance adjustment and a high-pressure VANOS line replacement, ensuring the valvetrain remains within tight tolerances for peak performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
