    {
      "id": "sybil_19_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_19",
      "description": "This 2018 Toyota 4Runner SR5 is a prime example of a well-maintained, dependable SUV. The exterior is finished in Classic Silver Metallic and retains a deep gloss, showing only minor stone chips and a light scuff on the rear bumper\u2014honest wear from careful daily use. Inside, the smoke-free cabin features graphite upholstery that remains firm and free of tears, with every button, dial, and the infotainment system performing exactly as they should. Under the hood, the V6 engine is remarkably clean; I have followed a strict maintenance schedule, including a recent oil change and brake inspection. The undercarriage is free of significant rust, and the vehicle sits on a set of high-quality all-terrain tires with plenty of life left. It drives straight, shifts smoothly, and offers a quiet, confident ride. This is a solid, turn-key vehicle for someone who values mechanical integrity and a clean, cared-for aesthetic.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
