    {
      "id": "sybil_18_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_18",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and she\u2019s been an absolute joy to drive. It's in really solid shape\u2014super clean inside and out, and it runs like a dream! I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with its next owner right away. If you're looking for something reliable that still looks fantastic and feels great on the road, this is the one for you. Feel free to shoot me a message if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
